      <span class="c-faq__title">What is Papyru?</span>
      <div class="c-faq__answer">
        <%= image_tag("logo.svg", alt: "", class: "c-faq__icon") %>
        <p class="c-faq__paragraph">With <strong>Papyru</strong> you can easily manage your education and fastly become more efficient<strong>.</strong></p>
        <p class="c-faq__paragraph">The entire app is organied by <span>subjects</span>: a <em>teacher</em> who subscribes can create a new channel for every subject he is teaching, a <em>student</em> can then be part of the channel when is added by the teacher<strong>.</strong></p>
        <p class="c-faq__paragraph">Every subject is splitted in different <span>topics</span>: in each one teachers and students can share new <em>messages</em>, <em>documents</em>, <em>communications</em>, <em>slides</em> and <em>other attachments</em><strong>.</strong></p>
      </div>
